The American Petroleum Institute, API,said its weekly U.S. petroleum inventory report will be issuedtonight, despite many company closures on Friday of last weekfor the Easter holiday.    The API report is usually released around 1700 EDT onTuesday nights.    The Energy Information Administration said it also expectsits weekly oil statistic report to be released as usual, onWednesday night at about 1700 EDT. Reuter&#3;